<p>We needed a way for hotels to directly communicate with guests, so we came up with a new two-way messaging platform. Working with one back end dev, I designed and developed the front end of this new web app. For this one, I had the chance to try out websockets and help implement a third-party API for SMS and MMS support.</p>

