<p>When our native guest services apps added support for opening hotel rooms with your phone, we needed a way to issue, activate, and deactivate mobile keys. Working with one back end dev, I designed and developed the front end of this new web app. I also built a small CSS framework during this project, which I would go on to use in most of my future projects at the company.</p>

<h3>
